---
const canchaItems = [
  {
    letter: "C",
    title: "Costos",
    text: "El oxígeno del equipo. Entiende tus números antes de pisar el césped.",
  },
  {
    letter: "A",
    title: "Audiencia",
    text: "Tu hincha barrabrava. Deja de venderle a todo el estadio.",
  },
  {
    letter: "N",
    title: "Narrativa",
    text: "Tu grito de batalla. Convierte tu marca en un imán.",
  },
  {
    letter: "C",
    title: "Cultura",
    text: "El ambiente del camerino. Tus valores innegociables.",
  },
  {
    letter: "H",
    title: "Habilidades",
    text: "El 10 del equipo. Domina tu estrategia y delega lo operativo.",
  },
  {
    letter: "A",
    title: "Acción",
    text: "El pitazo inicial. Ejecución imperfecta pero letal.",
  },
];
---

<section id="doble-motor" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-[#162741] px-4 py-20 text-white md:px-6 md:py-28">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(225,200,117,0.08),transparent_28%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,rgba(224,244,89,0.08),transparent_24%),linear-gradient(180deg,#162741_0%,#132238_100%)]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-white/8"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-white/8"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-[8%] top-16 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-[#E1C875]/8 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-[10%] top-24 h-52 w-52 rounded-full bg-[#e0f459]/8 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-[20px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#E1C875] md:text-2xl">
        La solución · El doble motor
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-5 text-[2.4rem] font-extrabold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.05em] text-white sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
        La arquitectura de tu victoria: El Doble Motor.
      </h2>

      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-white/72 md:text-[1.15rem] md:leading-9">
        El éxito requiere blindaje mental y ejecución pura.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <article class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border border-[#E1C875]/40 bg-white/4 p-7 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.22)] backdrop-blur-sm md:p-8">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-0 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-[#E1C875]/8 blur-2xl"></div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#E1C875]/35 bg-[#E1C875]/10 text-[#E1C875]">
  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2">
    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3l7 3v5c0 4.5-2.7 8.3-7 10-4.3-1.7-7-5.5-7-10V6l7-3z" />
    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.5 12l1.7 1.7L14.8 10" />
  </svg>
</div>

          <div>
            <p class="text-[15px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#E1C875] md:text-xl">
              Motor 1 · El Camerino
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-[-0.03em] text-white md:text-[2rem]">
              Blindaje mental antes de salir a jugar.
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-7 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-white/78 md:text-[1.05rem] md:leading-9">
          Entramos en tu cabeza para destruir el autosabotaje, el ego y las excusas que te impiden avanzar.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-[30px] border border-[#E1C875]/40 bg-white/4 p-7 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.22)] backdrop-blur-sm md:p-8">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-4 top-4 h-28 w-28 rounded-full bg-[#e0f459]/8 blur-2xl"></div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
         <div class="flex h-14 w-14 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#E1C875]/35 bg-[#E1C875]/10 text-[#E1C875]">
  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2">
    <rect x="4" y="5" width="16" height="14" rx="2" />
    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 9h.01M16 9h.01M8 15h.01" />
    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 15c2-1 3.5-2.5 5-5" />
    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12.7 9.8H14.8V11.9" />
  </svg>
</div>

          <div>
            <p class="text-[15px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#E1C875] md:text-xl">
              Motor 2 · La Cancha
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-[-0.03em] text-white md:text-[2rem]">
              El Método CANCHA para ejecutar sin humo.
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-7 text-base leading-8 text-white/78 md:text-[1.05rem] md:leading-9">
          Estas son las 6 dimensiones exactas que debes dominar:
        </p>

        <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-1">
          {canchaItems.map((item) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/8 bg-black/10 px-4 py-4">
              <span class="mt-0.5 inline-flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#e0f459] text-sm font-extrabold text-[#162741]">
                {item.letter}
              </span>
              <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-white/78 md:text-[0.98rem] md:leading-7">
                <span class="font-bold text-white">{item.title}:</span> {item.text}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-5xl rounded-[28px] border border-[#E1C875]/45 bg-[#0f1b2d]/78 p-6 shadow-[0_18px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.24)] md:p-8">
      <p class="text-[15px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#E1C875] md:text-2xl">
        El único balón
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-5xl text-xl font-bold leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.02em] text-[#ffffff] md:text-wxl md:leading-relaxed">
        Aquí no hay espacio para la dispersión. Te obligaré a elegir un solo proyecto (tu MVP) y a enfocarte exclusivamente en él durante 90 días.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
      <a
        href="/#pitazo-final"
        class="inline-flex min-h-[58px] items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#e0f459] px-8 text-sm font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#162741] shadow-[0_0_28px_rgba(224,244,89,0.22)] transition hover:-translate-y-px hover:shadow-[0_0_38px_rgba(224,244,89,0.32)]"
      >
        Quiero aplicar este método hoy
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
